sarahf: Yeah ‚Ä¶ so that Biden-Warren moment. What do you make of their exchange? Is this something we‚Äôre going to see replayed and that could hurt, say, Biden‚Äôs favorability? It definitely came across as a paternalistic moment, but I wonder if it will actually impact those who already support Biden., because aAs Julia mentioned in our pre-debate chat on Tuesday, and Perry on the live blog, ‚Äî part of what we‚Äôve learned through these debates is where in the party these candidates fall, and what that means as the party sorts out stances on race and gender.
