julia_azari: The Biden response to Warren‚Äôs point buries the point she was trying to make, which is to respond to all the pragmatism and implementation critiques throughout the night. She was trying to argue ‚Äúdream big, fight hard‚Äù ‚Äî and make the case for how and why that works.
