seth.masket: I think tonight was a big test for Warren, given her possible front-runner status, and she handled it well. So that‚Äôs a win. And yes, Klobuchar was given more time than usual and made the most of it.
geoffrey.skelley: I guess Harris might be a loser, too, in that I don‚Äôt see where she did much to break through again.
julia_azari: I agree with that.
